high_descs: Turn left towards the remote control on the coffee table.
Pick up the remote control from the coffee table.
Turn right and walk to the tall lamp in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Examine a remote control by the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Walk slightly forward and turn left to face the coffee table
Pick up the remote control from the coffee table
Turn right and walk up to the floor lamp in the corner
anns.task_desc: Examine the remote control under the light of the floor lamp

high_descs: Turn around to face the coffee table.
Pick up the remote control from the coffee table.
Turn right and carry the remote to the wall, then head right again to the lamp in the corner.
Turn on the lamp in the corner to look at the remote.
anns.task_desc: Examine the remote by the light of the lamp.
